  "texts": [
    "\"ARCAPA\" refers to \"Anomalous Right Coronary Artery Origin from Pulmonary Artery\".",
    "[CT] Smoothly bordered liver lesion of about 10 cm with density values of 20-30 HU.",
    "Clinically fever and upper abdominal pain.",
    "Left hepatic cholestasis and a gallstone can be identified.",
    "What are the most likely diagnoses?"
  ]
